                  <switch>
                    <use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#white-paper-blockchain-infrastructure"></use>
                  </switch>
                </svg>
                <span class="align-middle">OPENST WHITE PAPER</span>
              </a>
              <a href="https://github.com/OpenST/brandedtoken-contracts" class="github-link text-link ml-md-3 mt-3 mt-md-0" target="_blank" title="GITHUB">
                <svg width="15" height="15" class="align-middle">
                  <switch>
                    <use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#ost-block-chain-infra-github-icon"></use>
                  </switch>
                </svg>
                <span class="align-middle">GITHUB</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 info-card d-flex my-3 my-md-5">
          <div class="info-card-body p-3 pb-4 d-flex flex-column">
            <div style="flex: 1 1 auto;">
              <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                <svg width="35" height="35">
                  <switch>
                    <use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#ost-block-chain-infra-mosaic-logo"></use>
                  </switch>
                </svg>
                <h5>Scalability Protocol</h5>
              </div>
              <p>OpenST Mosaic introduces metablockchains to enable internet-grade transaction throughput on Ethereum. Your transactions run at lightning speed on auxiliary blockchains with economic finality secured asynchronously on Ethereum.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <a href="https://github.com/OpenSTFoundation/mosaic-contracts/blob/develop/docs/mosaicv0.pdf" class="white-paper-link text-link" target="_blank" title="WHITE PAPER">
